<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Amrita Vishwa Vidyapeetham</title>

    <style>
        body{
            margin:0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #8B0000, #B22222);
        }

        .container{
            width: 90%;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px gray;
        }

        h1{
            text-align: center;
            color: crimson;
        }

        .campus-links{
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .campus-links a{
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            color: black;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .campus-links a:hover{
            color: crimson;
        }

        .main{
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .login{
            width: 35%;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .login input, .login select{
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid gray;
        }

        .login button{
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background: black;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .about{
            width: 65%;
            background: #fafafa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .campus-content{
            display: none;
        }

        .campus-content:target{
            display: block;
        }

        .campus-content img{
            width: 70%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <h1>AMRITA VISHWA VIDYAPEETHAM</h1>

    <div class="campus-links">
        <a href="#amaravati">Amaravati</a>
        <a href="#amritapuri">Amritapuri</a>
        <a href="#chennai">Chennai</a>
        <a href="#coimbatore">Coimbatore</a>
        <a href="#mysore">Mysore</a>
        <a href="#bangalore">Bangalore</a>
    </div>

    <div class="main">

        <!-- Login Section -->
        <div class="login">
            <h3>Student Login</h3>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Username">
            <input type="password" placeholder="Password">
            <input type="email" placeholder="Enter Email" required>
            <input type="tel" placeholder="Enter Phone Number" required>

            <select required>
                <option value="">Select Course</option>
                <option>B.Tech</option>
                <option>M.Tech</option>
                <option>BCA</option>
                <option>MCA</option>
                <option>BBA</option>
                <option>MBA</option>
            </select>

            <button>Submit</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Campus Details Section -->
        <div class="about">
            <h3>About the Campus</h3>

            <div id="amaravati" class="campus-content">
                <img src="amrita.jpg.png" alt="Amaravati Campus">
                <h4>Amaravati Campus</h4>
                <p>Modern infrastructure and advanced engineering programs.A newer campus, expanding the university's presence in South India.</p>
            </div>

            <div id="amritapuri" class="campus-content">
                <img src="amritapuri.jpg.png" alt="Amritapuri Campus">
                <h4>Amritapuri Campus</h4>
                <p>Main campus located in Kerala known for research excellence.Known for engineering and biotechnology.Situated near the beach, it focuses on, for example, biotechnology, engineering, and spiritual-based education.</p>
            </div>

            <div id="chennai" class="campus-content">
                <img src="chennai.jpg.png" alt="Chennai Campus">
                <h4>Chennai Campus</h4>
                <p>Strong industry collaboration and technical programs.Offers various engineering programs.</p>
            </div>

            <div id="coimbatore" class="campus-content">
                <img src="coimbatoure.jpg.png" alt="Coimbatore Campus">
                <h4>Coimbatore Campus</h4>
                <p>Known for innovation and academic excellence.Administrative headquarters, engineering, and business schools.Located in Ettimadai, it is the administrative headquarters and houses the main Schools of Engineering and Business. It features a large, green campus with extensive infrastructure (libraries, labs).</p>
            </div>

            <div id="mysore" class="campus-content">
                <img src="mysore.jpg.png" alt="Mysore Campus">
                <h4>Mysore Campus</h4>
                <p>Focused on computing and engineering education.</p>
            </div>

            <div id="bangalore" class="campus-content">
                <img src="bangalore.jpg.png" alt="Bangalore Campus">
                <h4>Bangalore Campus</h4>
                <p>Offers management and technology programs.Focuses on engineering and technology. Focuses on technology, with strong placement opportunities and proximity to the tech hub.</p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>